<table class="infobox biography vcard" style="width:22em"><tbody><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold"><div class="fn" style="display:inline">Nicolai Abraham Abildgaard</div></th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_(1772,_Jens_Juel).jpg" class="image"><img alt="Der Maler Nicolai A. Abildgaard (1772, Jens Juel).jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_%281772%2C_Jens_Juel%29.jpg/200px-Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_%281772%2C_Jens_Juel%29.jpg" decoding="async" width="200" height="254" srcset="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_%281772%2C_Jens_Juel%29.jpg/300px-Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_%281772%2C_Jens_Juel%29.jpg 1.5x, http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_%281772%2C_Jens_Juel%29.jpg/400px-Der_Maler_Nicolai_A._Abildgaard_%281772%2C_Jens_Juel%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="639" data-file-height="813" /></a><div>Portrait of Nicolai Abildgaard by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jens_Juel_(painter)" title="Jens Juel (painter)">Jens Juel</a> (1772)</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Born</th><td><span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1743-09-11</span>)</span>September 11, 1743<sup id="cite_ref-EB_1-0" class="reference"><a href="Nicolai_Abildgaard#cite_note-EB-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><div style="display:inline" class="birthplace"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Copenhagen" title="Copenhagen">Copenhagen</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denmark" title="Denmark">Denmark</a></div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Died</th><td>June 4, 1809<span style="display:none">(1809-06-04)</span> (aged&#160;65)<sup id="cite_ref-EB_1-1" class="reference"><a href="Nicolai_Abildgaard#cite_note-EB-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><div style="display:inline" class="deathplace"><i>Spurveskjul</i> near <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frederiksdal_(Virum)" class="mw-redirect" title="Frederiksdal (Virum)">Frederiksdal</a>, Denmark</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Resting place</th><td class="label"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Assistens_Cemetery_(Copenhagen)" title="Assistens Cemetery (Copenhagen)">Assistens Cemetery</a>, Copenhagen</td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Nationality</th><td class="category">Danish</td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Education</th><td>New <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Royal_Danish_Academy_of_Art" class="mw-redirect" title="Royal Danish Academy of Art">Royal Danish Academy of Art</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Known&#160;for</th><td>Painting</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><b>Nicolai Abraham Abildgaard</b> (September 11, 1743&#160;– June 4, 1809)<sup id="cite_ref-EB_1-2" class="reference"><a href="Nicolai_Abildgaard#cite_note-EB-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> was a Danish <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoclassicism" title="Neoclassicism">neoclassical</a> and royal <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_painting" title="History painting">history painter</a>, sculptor, architect, and professor of painting, mythology, and anatomy at the New <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Royal_Danish_Academy_of_Art" class="mw-redirect" title="Royal Danish Academy of Art">Royal Danish Academy of Art</a> in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Copenhagen" title="Copenhagen">Copenhagen</a>, Denmark. Many of his works were in the royal <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christiansborg_Palace" title="Christiansborg Palace">Christiansborg Palace</a> (some destroyed by fire 1794), <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fredensborg_Palace" title="Fredensborg Palace">Fredensborg Palace</a>, and Levetzau Palace at <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amalienborg_Palace" class="mw-redirect" title="Amalienborg Palace">Amalienborg</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="Nicolai_Abildgaard#cite_note-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc" role="navigation" aria-labelledby="mw-toc-heading"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2 id="mw-toc-heading">Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
