<li id="cite_note-3"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Nicolai_Abildgaard#cite_ref-3">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFKatrine_Kalleklev" class="citation web">Katrine Kalleklev. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&amp;sl=no&amp;u=https://snl.no/S%25C3%25B8ren_Abildgaard&amp;prev=search">"Søren Abildgaard"</a>. Store norske leksikon<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">April  1,</span> 2019</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=S%C3%B8ren+Abildgaard&amp;rft.pub=Store+norske+leksikon&amp;rft.au=Katrine+Kalleklev&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com%2Ftranslate%3Fhl%3Den%26sl%3Dno%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsnl.no%2FS%2525C3%2525B8ren_Abildgaard%26prev%3Dsearch&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANicolai+Abildgaard" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
